-- Mozambique Sets Up Mechanism in Banks to Track Illegal Money, STV Reports
-- Fred Katerere
-- 2010-06-16T06:10:02Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/mozambique-sets-up-mechanism-in-banks-to-track-illegal-money-stv-reports.html

          
          
             Mozambican government has set up a
mechanism in banks and the finance ministry to monitor
circulation of illegal money, STV reported, citing Finance
Minister  Manuel Chang .  
 Chang said his ministry was aware the southern African
country was used a transit point by drug traffickers and money
launderers, STV reported.  
